Sage SkillsMap is a cloud-based, end-to-end recruitment solution that will modernise your recruitment processes.
The Sage Recruitment service will find the extraordinary amongst the ordinary. We don’t just place people; we offer you a customised, comprehensive recruitment solution to suit both your and the candidate’s needs.


Learn more about Sage Talent Solutions





Payroll Services


Payroll Outsourcing: Avoid the headaches. Let the professionals take care of your payroll. Learn More.
Payroll Consulting: Our Professional Services Division offers on-site payroll consulting services to clients who require one-on-one training and support. Learn More.
Project Consulting: Let us take charge of your software implementations with a dedicated team of professional project consultants. Learn More.
Special Solutions: We can create specialised solutions or reports for clients using (mostly) VIP Payroll data via ODBC connection. Learn More
Group Consultations: This is an incredibly cost-effective means of obtaining consulting assistance. We host up to six clients in a session and help you through the toughest times of the year. Learn More.


