Sage Conferencing

Flowing around an open street scape, Sage Conferencing is a modern, stylish and exquisitely finished centre that delivers on quality, exceptional food and elegant décor. 

Our facilities comprise six training rooms, one auditorium and two function venues with a capacity to host a confidential discussion, the training of small groups, a 150-delegate conference and cocktail parties for up to 300.
